&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;Alpha Health Care Limited are Dementia Specialists who are currently looking for a Senior Staff Nurse - Nights, experienced at Senior Lead level to join our Night team at Lakeview. The sucessful candidate will be responsible for leading and managing all elements of the unit, delivering excellent clinical care.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
